  "text": "Our algorithm consists of two parts, presented in two sections: In Section 4.1 we give a deterministic algorithm for constructing an overlay network such that it is sufficient to compute SSSP on this network. A randomized version of this result was given in [CITATION_1] . In Section 4.2 we present a more efficient algorithm for computing SSSP on this overlay network using Procedures 1 to 3 from before. We finish the computation in the same way as in [CITATION_2] .",
